{"tid":1814910,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[半年以來最大考驗] 不分化 不分化 不分化 不分化 不分化 不分化","createTime":"2020-01-07T06:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T08:30:39.000Z","uid":24178,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8f68e2c4ce1d918753141ed3738288f0f81e8900","tid":1814910,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"實在太撚緊要要講六次<br />\n我地無本錢再分化架喇<br />\n<br />\n無論你係每聽到槍聲就頭也不回咁跑上前去擋既勇武派<br />\n定係唔敢上前線但真係做到咩都唔割既進步和理非<br />\n定係只會係民陣吹雞先出 平時平行時空既14年和理非非 (呢班最要教育要進化)<br />\n<br />\n請你地緊記 你地選擇左既崗位係你地肯同可以為香港負出幾多既一個指標<br />\n我明大家各有自己既包袱 所以可以做既野都唔同亦都會驚<br />\n但所以點解先要慢慢一齊進步<br />\n勇武係6月9 日咪又係一個和理非 係612 逼我地去長大去進化 先至會去到今日<br />\n所以請大家多一啲體諒同埋解 小一啲指責同割蓆<br />\nWe are all in this together 所為和同勇只係大家進化既速度唔同<br />\n有人覺得仲有險可守 有人覺得已經要絕地反抗<br />\n只係觀點既分別 唔好係咪都屌同路人啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">最後致14年和理非一句說話: 真係咪撚捉鬼啦<br />\n你捉到夠唔夠薑真係殺撚左隻狗扮人?<br />\n到時咪又係夠喇夠喇 唔好再打喇會 輸民意<br />\n狗扮人做既所有野我地要食曬 係一個事實<br />\n就係咁唔公平 咁你又有扮狗做返啲野俾佢食?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛比分化強 與分化割蓆</span></span>"},{"pid":"c91682e37c55ce3f49ca5e7c67e05245b8962e9a","tid":1814910,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5033d4df2c7dbbe84e03b745a15210e0038d5733","tid":1814910,"uid":38164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"和勇一心！重新上陣！借鏡共產党革命思想！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814717</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">尊重勇武！<br />\n停止放負！<br />\n和勇一心！<br />\n重新上陣！<br />\n行動至上！</span></span>"},{"pid":"46e957d87f740c29bf931aeefe9d0bacf23c6cbf","tid":1814910,"uid":88133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"3754b860c0e7115959c0ccaa1c305046f4c889d3","tid":1814910,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"見咁多小隊呢排都退出，趁住呢個機會我地都⋯⋯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eJOesS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eJOesS</a>"},{"pid":"1a261740ecd53c8df00efdd19d7dece8bad80471","tid":1814910,"uid":288048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"真 行到今日係因為不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9905809bfd79303af4db7a12b28e59c32e24ebca","tid":1814910,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"325ff86d5962cff81a4b85476351d004adbd6dc8","tid":1814910,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:19:05.000Z","msg":"明有人會攰想休息<br />\n你休息我地會幫你頂住<br />\n休夠就出喇"},{"pid":"3f318d0a1a25036c06546d6b21c2978d5b4cce97","tid":1814910,"uid":263667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9A56ESg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9A56ESg.jpg&h=95129fbc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d8d6ed1e7e4401fac94549b94a468e97e1977b1","tid":1814910,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}